      "translation": "(1') To ..., ..., king of Urim , king of the four quarters , dedicated this ( vessel ) for his well-being ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001899.6",
      "line_range": "6",
      "translation": "(5') Whoever erases his inscription and writes his own name there , may Utu , king of Zimbir , put an end to his lineage !"
    }
